{"tid":2148652,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美艦現東海 華發佈英語驅趕敵機片","createTime":"2020-08-10T04:41:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-10T04:43:11.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e39218d1120f555376d54e97f41f9c1ff18a5bd4","tid":2148652,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T04:41:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200810/ZB56NPTT6XG2EYYJNVO4EKUKSA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200810%2FZB56NPTT6XG2EYYJNVO4EKUKSA%2F&d=V6cANorTbu7KkBEK5B25YicuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=14e8fe88\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200810%2FZB56NPTT6XG2EYYJNVO4EKUKSA%2F&h=992a75eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200810/ZB56NPTT6XG2EYYJNVO4EKUKSA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n美艦現東海 華發佈英語驅趕敵機片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/wqcBrobqtcAUp9pHmD5Ka2fxiDY=/539x406/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/36FGZQOBWTCMLWX7WUTBXN23JQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FwqcBrobqtcAUp9pHmD5Ka2fxiDY%3D%2F539x406%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F36FGZQOBWTCMLWX7WUTBXN23JQ.gif&h=6cce8d40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「列根號」航空母艦近日在東海巡航。<br />\n<br />\n美國衞生部長阿扎爾抵台前的一天，北京大學海洋研究院成立的智庫「南海戰略態勢感知計劃」披露，美軍「列根號」航空母艦和「安提頓號」導彈巡洋艦在日本與台灣之間的東海巡弋，與此同時大陸黨媒亦發佈解放軍飛行員向敵機「語音外逼」要求離開的片段。台灣國防部表示，這是大陸針對美國列根號上的艦載機作為假想敵，針對性相當濃厚，軍方已嚴密監控美航母及中共軍機的動態。<br />\n<br />\n針對列根號上艦載機<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：日前首相森喜朗率團弔唁李登輝<br />\n<br />\n南海戰略態勢感知計劃的Twitter昨上載「列根號」航空母艦和「安提頓號」巡洋艦在東海接近日本奄美大島水域游弋的衞星圖片，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n黨媒《人民日報》昨則在微博發佈解放軍軍機空中巡弋影片，強調飛行員發現。。。。。。。。。戒監視、查證識鳴、跟飛取證和語音警告，在最短時間內完成特情處置。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter/微博"},{"pid":"928fe4b7029aa59969c5641312abea2958e48da3","tid":2148652,"uid":5737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T04:43:11.000Z","msg":"咁咪好威？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}